&lt;p&gt;Palliative and End of Life Care Clinical Lead - 4 months fixed term contract or secondment to 31 March 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The East of England Regional Nursing Directorate is seeking to appoint a Palliative and End of Life Care Clinical Lead on a part time basis (2 PAs / 7.5 hours per week). The Clinical Lead role will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide clinical leadership for the region’s managed network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with and support the clinical leads in the CCG’s/STPs/ICSs within the region&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the National Palliative and End of Life Care programme, including supporting or taking the lead on specific projects as agreed with the National Clinical Director and representation on the Palliative and End of Life Care Operational Board.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that the reason for the fixed term of your contract is short term project due to funding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to COVID-19 restrictions NHS England/Improvement employees are currently working from home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shortlisting will be completed within one week of the advert closing, with interviews taking place during the following fortnight (ie within 3 weeks of the advert close date).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Frances Bolger&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Clinical Quality Director&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: frances.bolger@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 07388 007613&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Frances Bolger, Clinical Quality Director - frances.bolger@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
